datasets.name: AISP One & Two Year Tyvek Tag Dealers
datasets.description: Where to get the Aquatic Invasive Species Prevention Permit.  All boats 10 feet long and longer (canoes, kayaks, drift boats, inflatable boats, etc.), out-of-state motor boats, and sailboats are required to purchase and carry an AISP permit when operating a watercraft on Oregon's waterways.
